parameters.description:
Enter JSON key values to filter the alert response, from Claroty, based on the specified parameters. 
For example, {"asset_id__exact": "122", "severity__exact": 4} 
The list of fields that can be used as keys on the filters paramaters page are: per_page, asset_id__exact, asset__exact, for_asset__exact, q__exact, primary_asset__exact, non_primary_assets__exact, virtual_zone__exact, alert_id__exact, ot_alerts__exact, family__exact, story_severity__exact, id__exact, site_id__exact, data__exact, description__exact, type__exact, category__exact, severity__exact, timestamp__exact, relevant__exact, resolved__exact, resolution__exact, protocol__exact, score__exact, is_qualified__exact, network_id__exact, resolved_id__exact, assigned_id__exact, story_id__exact, or sort
